<author>Thangngur</author>
<title>Ka Chawl Ta le</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mun zek a hi hiel tam ka pienna nuoi simlei,
 Chung sunni lenkawla a hung suok zat in Aw;
 Albang dah leh lungkham na'n ei bawm ie.

[V2]
 Ka chawl ta ie (2)
 Ei suonte bawhsiet zieka lei hansedawl hi;
 Ka chawl ta ie (2)
 Gikpuok ei dawn zang ding guolpha ka ngai ,

[V3]
 2. Sim leh mal ka hawl viela guolpha ka mu puoi ,
 Gimumna hung lienin ka neihsun a lamang;
 Van Lal Immanuel A hung nai ie.

[V4]
 Zie hi A gen (2)
 &quot;Ka cha na gikpuok ka keng bulah hung nga than&quot;
 Zie hi A gen (2)
 &quot;Ka khut ka keng enin, chun zang in la&quot;

[V5]
 3. Ka ngaihpen ka muhin ka gikpuok ei dawn zang,
 Sietlei hansie cheng puo'n Kalvari-ah A mau;
 Aman ka gikpuok cheng ei dawn zang tai.

[V6]
 Gen thiem leng aw (2)
 Kei banga puokgik leh mi lungkhamte kiengah;
 Gen thiem leng aw (2)
 A hehpihna thuk zie leh a sanzie.

[V7]
 4. Lei Lalpa gam ei puoi, ka tha a muong thei puoi ,
 A na khuksak u kha linglukhuk ahi maw?
 A chiehna haksa mahleh zui ingka.

[V8]
 Ei phal puon a (2)
 Amah lunga ngilh a khawvel pak tan ding chu;
 Ei phal puon a (2)
 Amah beia albang ka vaih ding chu.</lyrics>
</song>